This plugin helps you creating lot of dynamic code used in your pages, but in Groovy, instead of javascript.
Will speed up your developing, working with the tools you know, like Spock, Codenarc, Gradle,...
Also use Vert.x for reloading pages and give you an event tool between server and browser.

h2. Important

This plugin still in development. Is not production ready, the Groovy code not need to be converted if your source
files not changing. Javascript code have to be inserted in the pages.

h2. Requisites

You need *Java 1.7+* to use the plugin. Vert.x requires it.
